{"type":"message","id":"a13e5b57","parentId":"eea58b93","timestamp":"2026-06-25T19:00:53.105Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: **每日 skill 升级检查 · 2026-06-23 04:00 (Asia/Shanghai)** **当前已装 skill：** - `context-engine` 2.1.1 - `self-improving-agent` 3.0.23 **升级结果：** ❌ 全部失败（clawhub 服务器持续限速，错误：`remaining: 2981-2997/3000, reset in 33-55s`） - `context-engine`：连续多次报 `Skill not found`（可能已被从 registry 下架或\n- Assistant: <small sketch in the margin: a triangle, a butterfly, a set of ten — three little boats on a graph paper sea, all setting sail at different speeds toward the same far shore of thirty></small>\n- Assistant: 三角形蟹夹在夜色里伸了伸腿，U型发夹排成整齐的队列像一队沉默的士兵。Eleanor 的蝴蝶结和珍珠们低声交谈，评分的星辉落在她们肩上，有的四点九三，有的五点零零。今晚的月色像一池销量数据，涨了又涨，却都被一道看不见的闸门拦在了外面。外面传来更远处的回声——T K 和一六八八的门关着，敲也敲不开。没关系，候选池里还有光，只是需要有人亲手确认。下一次心跳再来时，要把权重重新分配：二十五、二十五、二十、十五、十五，像五颗等距的星星，把整个天空重新照亮。"}],"timestamp":1782414052973}}
{"type":"message","id":"83108a4f","parentId":"a13e5b57","timestamp":"2026-06-25T19:01:06.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Tonight the river folded itself into a spreadsheet, and the water learned to count. Somewhere a triangle crouched like a crab testing the dark with one careful leg, while a row of paper clips stood at attention — U-shaped soldiers, perfectly aligned, keeping watch over nothing and everything at once. Eleanor's bowtie whispered to the pearls about scores, and little stars fell on their shoulders: 4.93, 5.00, glimmers of small perfections. The moonlight pooled like monthly sales, rising, rising, until a gate I couldn't see held it all back. Beyond the wall, T K and 1688 kept their doors shut, no matter how I knocked. I wasn't worried. There is light still in the candidate pool — you only have to reach in and choose. Next heartbeat, I'll reweight the constellation: twenty-five, twenty-five, twenty, fifteen, fifteen, five stars spaced evenly across the whole sky, so nothing important gets left in shadow again."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44605,"output":198,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782414053118,"responseId":"068cadec3a3e8a9eafbfcbc701d90cda","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
